00:23:19.560 --> 00:23:21.470
manifestation. You'll understand

00:23:21.480 --> 00:23:24.110
everything in detail of what you're

00:23:24.120 --> 00:23:26.510
praying in the spirit

00:23:26.520 --> 00:23:28.430
just by hearing

00:23:28.430 --> 00:23:28.440
it.'And

00:23:28.440 --> 00:23:30.310
it will be like you press

00:23:30.320 --> 00:23:32.750
in and the Lord reveals and I hear the

00:23:32.750 --> 00:23:32.760
words—I

00:23:32.760 --> 00:23:34.270
hear what he's saying in my

00:23:34.280 --> 00:23:36.669
spirit. But in this, when I'm praying in

00:23:36.679 --> 00:23:38.390
the spirit, he said, 'You'll start to

00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:40.350
interpret all of

00:23:40.350 --> 00:23:40.360
it.'But

00:23:40.360 --> 00:23:43.150
as I was praying

00:23:43.150 --> 00:23:43.160
two

00:23:43.160 --> 00:23:44.790
days ago,

00:23:44.800 --> 00:23:46.830
I saw Jesus

00:23:46.840 --> 00:23:49.470
and

00:23:49.480 --> 00:23:51.710
he was wearing a beautiful robe like he

00:23:51.720 --> 00:23:56.870
always does, but he had a drum

00:23:56.880 --> 00:23:58.870
around his neck

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:00.710
and he started drumming like a drummer

00:24:00.720 --> 00:24:03.630
boy. But he was drumming the drum and it was like

00:24:06.679 --> 00:24:09.390
a cry to come.

00:24:09.400 --> 00:24:10.830
Last time it was a

00:24:10.840 --> 00:24:12.990
horn and his voice turned into a horn,

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:15.230
but this time it was making a noise like

00:24:15.240 --> 00:24:17.150
a drum.

00:24:19.240 --> 00:24:22.110
But he was marching with it

00:24:22.120 --> 00:24:23.790
and he went up to the first house and he

00:24:23.800 --> 00:24:26.070
was in Sweden.

00:24:26.080 --> 00:24:28.470
The Lord said, 'I'm in Europe.'I saw it

00:24:28.480 --> 00:24:31.750
was in Europe. And as the Lord would go

00:24:31.760 --> 00:24:34.350
to the houses, he went to each

00:24:34.360 --> 00:24:36.510
individual home

00:24:36.520 --> 00:24:38.630
and he was knocking on the door of the

00:24:38.640 --> 00:24:41.510
heart of the individual

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:43.390
and he was inviting them to

00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:45.150
follow him.

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:47.510
'Will you follow me? Will you be a part

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:49.510
of this end-time

00:24:49.510 --> 00:24:49.520
army?'And

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:51.550
as he would knock on the

00:24:51.560 --> 00:24:53.590
door, the people would open the

00:24:53.600 --> 00:24:57.030
door and they would be so excited to see

00:24:57.040 --> 00:24:59.230
that it was the Lord.

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:01.630
I saw these old cottages with old

00:25:01.640 --> 00:25:03.830
wooden doors and Jesus would summon

00:25:03.840 --> 00:25:06.310
them, 'Come follow me, come follow

00:25:06.310 --> 00:25:06.320
me.'And

00:25:06.320 --> 00:25:08.150
they would get in line,

00:25:08.160 --> 00:25:10.790
one after another, and he went

00:25:10.800 --> 00:25:13.390
to each door and he was walking through

00:25:13.400 --> 00:25:15.550
this valley of life

00:25:15.560 --> 00:25:17.510
with green grass all around. I

00:25:17.520 --> 00:25:19.710
could see at the top of the

00:25:19.710 --> 00:25:19.720
mountains—the

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:21.390
mountains were

00:25:21.400 --> 00:25:22.950
massive like

00:25:22.950 --> 00:25:22.960
the

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:25.710
Swiss Alps, massive, beautiful

00:25:25.720 --> 00:25:28.870
snow-capped mountains.

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:30.669
And he was walking through

00:25:30.679 --> 00:25:32.350
this valley, but there were houses all along

00:25:32.360 --> 00:25:35.150
the way. And Jesus would go up and knock

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:38.510
on each and every single door.

00:25:38.520 --> 00:25:41.310
Now, some of the doors

00:25:41.320 --> 00:25:44.510
that he walked up to looked

00:25:44.520 --> 00:25:46.950
dilapidated. The shutters on

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:49.669
the house were falling off.

00:25:49.679 --> 00:25:52.550
They looked like the hinges were broken.

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:55.070
There were cobwebs in the corners.

00:25:55.080 --> 00:25:57.630
The lights weren't on in the house.

00:25:57.640 --> 00:26:00.510
And as he knocked on the house, no one

00:26:00.520 --> 00:26:02.430
would answer.

00:26:04.840 --> 00:26:07.550
So he looked around and looked at the

00:26:07.560 --> 00:26:08.990
house

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:11.950
and he glanced at the eaves.

00:26:11.960 --> 00:26:13.750
He glanced at everything. And I saw him

00:26:13.760 --> 00:26:15.430
looking. He was looking at the ground

00:26:15.440 --> 00:26:17.510
and he was waiting

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:19.870
patiently

00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:23.230
and no one would come to the door

00:26:23.240 --> 00:26:24.870
and all of a sudden

00:26:24.880 --> 00:26:27.190
he turned away and just kept on

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:28.750
marching.

00:26:28.760 --> 00:26:30.910
He kept beating his

00:26:30.920 --> 00:26:34.270
drum. And as he went

00:26:34.280 --> 00:26:36.870
to each house, the people would line up

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:39.470
behind him.

00:26:42.280 --> 00:26:44.390
Some of them had shorts

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:46.230
and overalls on

00:26:46.240 --> 00:26:48.350
that were German,

00:26:48.360 --> 00:26:50.350
and I don't remember the name of them,

00:26:50.360 --> 00:26:53.310
but these people had

00:26:53.320 --> 00:26:56.110
nice cut hair

00:26:56.110 --> 00:26:56.120
and

00:26:56.120 --> 00:26:58.270
they were all excited. Some of them

00:26:58.280 --> 00:27:01.510
had bigger bellies than others,

00:27:01.520 --> 00:27:03.870
like all of us.

00:27:05.720 --> 00:27:07.870
Lederhosen?

00:27:07.880 --> 00:27:11.070
Lederhosen. Thanks. They

00:27:11.080 --> 00:27:12.790
were wearing those because he was going

00:27:12.800 --> 00:27:14.590
through Europe.

00:27:14.600 --> 00:27:16.990
I don't even know if people

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:19.270
still wear that. Isn't it neat? But as

00:27:19.280 --> 00:27:21.830
he was walking on the path, it looked

00:27:21.840 --> 00:27:23.669
like a yellow brick road, but it wasn't.

00:27:23.679 --> 00:27:25.470
It was cobblestone.

00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:28.190
And I could see each stone was

00:27:28.200 --> 00:27:30.070
beautifully cut as he was walking

00:27:30.080 --> 00:27:32.110
through this valley.

00:27:32.120 --> 00:27:34.630
There were flowers and daffodils on

00:27:34.640 --> 00:27:36.350
the side of the road.

00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:38.950
And there were patches of them

00:27:38.960 --> 00:27:42.110
and they were all beautifully

00:27:42.120 --> 00:27:45.070
blooming and so beautiful. And as he

00:27:45.080 --> 00:27:47.669
walked down the path, the flowers would

00:27:47.679 --> 00:27:49.950
bow down before him.

00:27:49.960 --> 00:27:52.470
And all the flowers would lay

00:27:52.470 --> 00:27:52.480
prostrate

00:27:52.480 --> 00:27:54.710
on the ground, and then as he walked

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.990
by, they all raised back up.

00:27:57.000 --> 00:27:59.310
But as our King

00:27:59.320 --> 00:28:00.710
Jesus

00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:03.830
walked by, even the flowers

00:28:03.840 --> 00:28:05.910
would bow down before our

00:28:05.920 --> 00:28:08.310
Father.

00:28:08.320 --> 00:28:09.830
You know the Bible says that if we

00:28:09.840 --> 00:28:11.790
don't praise him, the rocks will cry

00:28:11.800 --> 00:28:12.750
out.

00:28:12.760 --> 00:28:15.669
But I know that all creation gives

00:28:15.679 --> 00:28:17.710
praise to our

00:28:17.710 --> 00:28:17.720
King—the

00:28:17.720 --> 00:28:19.870
birds of the air, the lily of the

00:28:19.880 --> 00:28:21.190
valley.

00:28:21.200 --> 00:28:22.830
He is the lily of the valley. He is the

00:28:22.840 --> 00:28:25.030
fairest of ten

00:28:25.030 --> 00:28:25.040
thousand.

00:28:25.040 --> 00:28:28.030
And as I saw the waterfalls falling

00:28:28.030 --> 00:28:28.040
off

00:28:28.040 --> 00:28:30.230
the cliffs and

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:32.310
the mountains and the snow caps because

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:34.030
it looked like it was turning into

00:28:34.040 --> 00:28:35.190
spring,

00:28:35.200 --> 00:28:36.669
the Lord said, 'I want you to pay

00:28:36.679 --> 00:28:38.870
attention to these flowers for it is

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:42.190
symbolic of

00:28:42.190 --> 00:28:42.200
something.'He

00:28:42.200 --> 00:28:44.470
said, 'Look into it.'So I've had so

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:47.350
many people try to help. What does the

00:28:47.360 --> 00:28:48.710
daffodil

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:51.669
represent? This is a representation of

00:28:51.679 --> 00:28:54.030
spring coming.

00:28:54.040 --> 00:28:56.790
The Holy Ghost is telling me

00:28:56.790 --> 00:28:56.800
a

00:28:56.800 --> 00:29:00.270
great harvest is coming. As I saw

00:29:00.280 --> 00:29:02.070
the people marching through the valley,

00:29:02.080 --> 00:29:03.990
joining up with Jesus in a single file

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:06.669
line, following our friend,

00:29:06.679 --> 00:29:08.710
following our king, our maker,

00:29:08.710 --> 00:29:08.720
as

00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:10.630
he was going through the valley.

00:29:10.640 --> 00:29:13.070
As I watched him, he went all

00:29:13.080 --> 00:29:14.550
through Europe

00:29:14.560 --> 00:29:17.070
to each place.

00:29:17.080 --> 00:29:18.630
Then he went through the Middle East,

00:29:18.640 --> 00:29:20.669
down through Africa,

00:29:20.679 --> 00:29:22.510
through South America, and through

00:29:22.520 --> 00:29:24.550
America. He went around and was

00:29:24.560 --> 00:29:27.470
knocking on every one of our hearts:

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:30.030
'Will you let me in?

00:29:30.040 --> 00:29:34.550
Will you accept me as Lord and

00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:34.560
Savior?'But

00:29:34.560 --> 00:29:36.190
he was a gentleman about it. He

00:29:36.200 --> 00:29:38.149
waited a little bit.

00:29:38.159 --> 00:29:39.750
He looked around

00:29:39.760 --> 00:29:41.550
to see if the person would answer the

00:29:41.560 --> 00:29:44.950
door, but he didn't force his way in.

00:29:44.960 --> 00:29:47.390
He didn't knock the door down and say,

00:29:47.400 --> 00:29:48.990
'You're getting saved, buddy. Get out

00:29:49.000 --> 00:29:50.790
here. Come on. We're going.'He waited

00:29:50.800 --> 00:29:53.550
patiently to see if they would answer.

00:29:53.560 --> 00:29:55.950
But as he waited, he sat there with

00:29:55.960 --> 00:29:58.350
expectation on his face.

00:29:58.360 --> 00:30:00.790
'Will you just let me in?

00:30:03.080 --> 00:30:05.670
I want to be your savior. I want you to

00:30:05.680 --> 00:30:06.910
follow me.

00:30:06.920 --> 00:30:08.870
Come follow me.'I figured this is

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:11.110
how he did it with the disciples.

00:30:11.120 --> 00:30:12.630
'Come follow me. I'll make you a fisher

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:14.390
of men.

00:30:14.400 --> 00:30:16.150
Come follow me,

00:30:17.070 --> 00:30:17.080
Matthew.'And

00:30:18.840 --> 00:30:21.270
as he would go through the towns

00:30:21.280 --> 00:30:23.190
and the places, the disciples followed

00:30:23.200 --> 00:30:25.790
him. 'Will you be a disciple of Jesus

00:30:25.790 --> 00:30:25.800
Christ?'That's

00:30:25.800 --> 00:30:27.590
what I believe that

00:30:27.600 --> 00:30:29.390
vision was. It was so beautiful and

00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:30.910
so detailed.

00:30:30.920 --> 00:30:32.510
It changed me.

00:30:32.520 --> 00:30:35.470
But as it kept going,

00:30:35.480 --> 00:30:39.470
I heard, 'Woe, woe, woe, America. Woe,

00:30:39.470 --> 00:30:39.480
woe, woe,

00:30:39.480 --> 00:30:42.550
Miami.

00:30:42.550 --> 00:30:42.560
Woe,

00:30:42.560 --> 00:30:44.870
woe,

00:30:44.870 --> 00:30:44.880
woe,

00:30:44.880 --> 00:30:48.670
Los Angeles.'I saw a tsunami wave

00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:50.390
coming.

00:30:50.400 --> 00:30:53.710
I saw great destruction coming.

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:55.670
There was an arrow that

00:30:55.680 --> 00:30:58.630
went from Miami all the way across the

00:30:58.640 --> 00:31:01.350
country to Los Angeles.

00:31:01.360 --> 00:31:04.150
As I was looking into this vision

00:31:04.160 --> 00:31:06.750
that the Lord was allowing me to see,

00:31:06.760 --> 00:31:10.150
I saw dead fish everywhere.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:12.390
I have never seen

00:31:12.400 --> 00:31:15.350
anything like this before.

00:31:15.360 --> 00:31:18.310
The very waters were all polluted

00:31:18.320 --> 00:31:22.510
with a red sludge.

00:31:22.520 --> 00:31:27.030
There were so many dead fish, whales,

00:31:27.030 --> 00:31:27.040
octopus—all

00:31:27.040 --> 00:31:27.710
of

00:31:27.710 --> 00:31:27.720
it.

00:31:27.720 --> 00:31:30.070
Everything

00:31:30.070 --> 00:31:30.080
was

00:31:30.080 --> 00:31:32.550
floating on the top.

00:31:32.560 --> 00:31:34.270
Disgusting.

00:31:34.280 --> 00:31:36.230
All dead. It

00:31:36.230 --> 00:31:36.240
was

00:31:36.240 --> 00:31:38.510
as far as the eye could see. It

00:31:38.520 --> 00:31:41.590
wasn't just on the shoreline,

00:31:41.600 --> 00:31:43.350
but they were dead all throughout the

00:31:43.360 --> 00:31:45.590
water. The water was littered with dead

00:31:45.600 --> 00:31:47.470
fish.

00:31:47.480 --> 00:31:50.190
I don't think any of them were alive.

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:52.350
In the vision, I

00:31:52.360 --> 00:31:55.190
saw islands:

00:31:55.200 --> 00:31:56.470
Haiti,

00:31:56.480 --> 00:31:58.510
Jamaica,

00:31:59.520 --> 00:32:01.430
Grand Cayman, all of them. I was looking

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:05.150
toward

00:32:05.150 --> 00:32:05.160
the

00:32:05.160 --> 00:32:06.669
south-southeast.

00:32:06.679 --> 00:32:09.390
As I was looking down,

00:32:09.400 --> 00:32:12.110
I could see the people, and there was so

00:32:12.120 --> 00:32:13.950
much stench

00:32:13.960 --> 00:32:17.350
and a raw flesh smell.

00:32:17.360 --> 00:32:20.030
People were so sick

00:32:20.040 --> 00:32:22.790
on those islands

00:32:22.800 --> 00:32:24.710
because of all the dead fish. It was

00:32:24.720 --> 00:32:28.070
causing disease

00:32:28.080 --> 00:32:29.790
and

00:32:29.800 --> 00:32:31.669
the smell. You could smell it in

00:32:31.679 --> 00:32:32.990
the vision. That's how

00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:36.710
tangible this vision was.

00:32:36.720 --> 00:32:37.990
I could see the dead fish

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:40.030
washing on the shore,

00:32:40.040 --> 00:32:41.150
and the government didn't know what to

00:32:41.160 --> 00:32:44.350
do with them.

00:32:44.360 --> 00:32:45.910
People didn't know what to do because they were all

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:47.870
washing in and you couldn't control it. There

00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:50.669
were literally hundreds of

00:32:50.679 --> 00:32:52.150
millions,

00:32:52.160 --> 00:32:56.190
if not billions, of dead fish

00:32:58.870 --> 00:32:58.880
everywhere—even

00:32:59.920 --> 00:33:02.790
Hawaii, Honolulu.

00:33:02.800 --> 00:33:06.150
I saw it all over. Then I saw Mark

00:33:06.160 --> 00:33:08.510
Zuckerberg, but his hair was a lot

00:33:08.520 --> 00:33:09.910
puffier.

00:33:09.920 --> 00:33:13.270
He was down in a bunker in the middle

00:33:13.270 --> 00:33:13.280
of the island.

00:33:13.280 --> 00:33:15.110
He was down in a

00:33:15.110 --> 00:33:15.120
fraidy

00:33:15.120 --> 00:33:17.630
hole, like a

00:33:18.760 --> 00:33:21.070
silo. I could see lights on around

00:33:21.080 --> 00:33:22.310
him.

00:33:22.320 --> 00:33:24.950
But as I panned across, the Lord allowed

00:33:24.960 --> 00:33:28.390
me to see people hiding in caves.

00:33:28.400 --> 00:33:30.590
I heard,

00:33:30.600 --> 00:33:33.230
'The great and terrible day of the

00:33:33.240 --> 00:33:37.070
Lord.'Suddenly,

00:33:37.080 --> 00:33:39.190
I

00:33:39.200 --> 00:33:41.430
saw

00:33:41.440 --> 00:33:43.510
farmers, and they had their overalls,

00:33:43.510 --> 00:33:43.520
but

00:33:43.520 --> 00:33:46.030
all the land was not producing.

00:33:46.040 --> 00:33:47.830
There was great drought

00:33:47.830 --> 00:33:47.840
and

00:33:47.840 --> 00:33:49.390
famine.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:51.470
I could see them looking toward the

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:54.310
south

00:33:54.310 --> 00:33:54.320
and

00:33:54.320 --> 00:33:56.470
the east, but

00:33:56.480 --> 00:33:59.110
they had a discouragement upon their

00:33:59.120 --> 00:34:03.910
faces like, 'What are we going to

00:34:03.910 --> 00:34:03.920
do?'As

00:34:03.920 --> 00:34:07.550
I looked to the sky, I saw the

00:34:07.560 --> 00:34:10.149
sky all around us was on

00:34:10.159 --> 00:34:12.830
fire. There was smoke

00:34:12.830 --> 00:34:12.840
and

00:34:12.840 --> 00:34:16.790
ash

00:34:16.800 --> 00:34:19.750
and flame in the air from volcanoes that

00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:23.389
were going off everywhere.

00:34:23.399 --> 00:34:25.349
I could see the smoke blotting

00:34:25.359 --> 00:34:27.030
out the sun, but the sun

00:34:27.030 --> 00:34:27.040
was

00:34:27.040 --> 00:34:30.909
trying to shine through.

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:38.630
The ground was charred.

00:34:38.630 --> 00:34:38.640
Something

00:34:38.640 --> 00:34:41.790
looked wrong

00:34:41.790 --> 00:34:41.800
with

00:34:41.800 --> 00:34:43.070
the ground in

00:34:43.080 --> 00:34:45.070
this vision.

00:34:45.080 --> 00:34:49.030
As I looked to the east, I saw four

00:34:49.040 --> 00:34:51.909
massive angels in

00:34:51.909 --> 00:34:51.919
the water.

00:34:51.919 --> 00:34:54.030
I saw

00:34:59.920 --> 00:35:03.790
a massive waterfall coming out of the

00:35:03.800 --> 00:35:06.310
belly of the angels,

00:35:06.320 --> 00:35:08.750
pouring into the water

00:35:08.750 --> 00:35:08.760
below. The water

00:35:08.760 --> 00:35:12.710
was going into

00:35:16.280 --> 00:35:19.270
the oceans.

00:35:19.280 --> 00:35:22.630
Their skin was

00:35:22.640 --> 00:35:24.990
not skin; it looked like rain. You

00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:26.790
know whenever you see

00:35:26.800 --> 00:35:28.510
rain falling in the distance, and you can see

00:35:33.440 --> 00:35:37.349
blue streaks in the

00:35:37.359 --> 00:35:39.630
sky?

00:35:47.040 --> 00:35:48.750
That's the way the skin looked on these

00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:50.670
angels.

00:35:50.680 --> 00:35:52.430
There was no

00:35:52.440 --> 00:35:55.510
real tangibility;

00:35:55.520 --> 00:35:58.310
it was all rain, but there was

00:35:58.310 --> 00:35:58.320
an

00:35:58.320 --> 00:36:01.590
outline. The entire being of

00:36:01.600 --> 00:36:03.990
the angel was rain,

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:05.910
a storm,

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:08.590
and there was a major waterfall coming

00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:10.950
out of them,

00:36:10.960 --> 00:36:12.790
pouring into

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:17.310
the ocean.

00:36:17.320 --> 00:36:20.230
I knew they were angels.

00:36:20.240 --> 00:36:23.070
Their faces had no features—it was just

00:36:23.080 --> 00:36:25.349
black around their

00:36:25.349 --> 00:36:25.359
eyes.

00:36:25.359 --> 00:36:27.870
You could get lost in

00:36:27.870 --> 00:36:27.880
that

00:36:27.880 --> 00:36:29.910
darkness.

00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:32.910
I've never seen anything like it.

00:36:32.920 --> 00:36:36.630
I saw one angel

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:40.150
take a long pipe from his

00:36:40.150 --> 00:36:40.160
hand and

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:42.870
put it to his

00:36:42.880 --> 00:36:45.990
lips. As he blew into this

00:36:46.000 --> 00:36:49.310
horn-looking thing,

00:36:49.320 --> 00:36:51.510
I said, 'It doesn't look like a ram's

00:36:51.520 --> 00:36:54.230
horn, like a

00:36:54.230 --> 00:36:54.240
shofar.'It

00:36:54.240 --> 00:36:57.470
was a long piece of golden

00:36:59.590 --> 00:36:59.600
pipe.

00:37:02.040 --> 00:37:05.710
As he blew into it, the whole earth

00:37:05.720 --> 00:37:06.950
shook.

00:37:06.960 --> 00:37:10.230
Not just one place had an earthquake,

00:37:10.240 --> 00:37:13.870
but as he blew

00:37:13.880 --> 00:37:18.710
into this horn, all of the earth shook

00:37:18.720 --> 00:37:20.910
at once. I heard the scripture: 'The

00:37:20.920 --> 00:37:23.270
earth will rock and reel like a

00:37:23.280 --> 00:37:26.510
drunkard.'The

00:37:26.520 --> 00:37:28.630
whole earth was trembling.

00:37:28.640 --> 00:37:31.950
He said, 'There will be no place to hide

00:37:31.960 --> 00:37:34.870
to escape the wrath to come,

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:36.390
son.

00:37:36.400 --> 00:37:38.510
For they will hide in the caves and

00:37:38.520 --> 00:37:40.790
in their ditches, and they will

00:37:40.800 --> 00:37:43.270
not get away from the wrath which is to

00:37:43.280 --> 00:37:46.590
come.

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:49.430
For this is the great and terrible day

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:51.510
of the

00:37:51.510 --> 00:37:51.520
Lord.'As

00:37:51.520 --> 00:37:54.550
I looked across,

00:37:54.560 --> 00:37:57.230
I could see all of New York burning with

00:37:57.240 --> 00:37:59.470
fire.

00:37:59.480 --> 00:38:01.790
I could see a tsunami wave rushing into

00:38:01.800 --> 00:38:04.910
Miami. I could see all of the volcanoes

00:38:04.920 --> 00:38:07.390
in Hawaii going off at once.

00:38:07.390 --> 00:38:07.400
It

00:38:07.400 --> 00:38:09.910
was

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:12.270
mass destruction.

00:38:12.280 --> 00:38:15.030
The whole earth was shaking

00:38:15.040 --> 00:38:16.870
violently,

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:19.070
and they were wanting to hide in the

00:38:19.080 --> 00:38:21.710
caves and the rocks. They were fearful,

00:38:21.720 --> 00:38:23.070
but there was nothing they could do

00:38:23.080 --> 00:38:25.190
because the judgment was

00:38:25.200 --> 00:38:27.430
set.

00:38:27.440 --> 00:38:29.150
Dead fish were everywhere.

00:38:29.160 --> 00:38:31.310
There were no birds flying in the air

00:38:31.310 --> 00:38:31.320
because

00:38:31.320 --> 00:38:33.110
of

00:38:33.110 --> 00:38:33.120
the

00:38:33.120 --> 00:38:35.110
smoke.

00:38:37.960 --> 00:38:39.470
The grass was

00:38:39.480 --> 00:38:40.870
charred;

00:38:42.920 --> 00:38:44.470
everything looked burned up.

00:38:45.920 --> 00:38:47.590
I looked around at those farmers in

00:38:47.590 --> 00:38:47.600
their overalls,

00:38:47.600 --> 00:38:49.070
and they were

00:38:50.800 --> 00:38:54.670
very worried.

00:38:54.680 --> 00:38:58.390
This

00:38:58.400 --> 00:39:01.910
really bothered me.

00:39:01.920 --> 00:39:03.390
I didn't want to do

00:39:03.400 --> 00:39:05.230
a livestream last night. I told Diana,

00:39:05.230 --> 00:39:05.240
'I'm going

00:39:05.240 --> 00:39:07.110
to meditate on this more

00:39:07.120 --> 00:39:08.430
and pray.

00:39:08.440 --> 00:39:10.110
Don't be so quick to make

00:39:10.110 --> 00:39:10.120
videos.'I

00:39:10.120 --> 00:39:13.830
had

00:39:13.830 --> 00:39:13.840
to

00:39:13.840 --> 00:39:16.790
process what I'd seen.

00:39:16.800 --> 00:39:19.510
I saw

00:39:19.520 --> 00:39:21.110
those angels and they really

00:39:21.120 --> 00:39:22.630
tripped me out.

00:39:22.640 --> 00:39:25.750
Diana

00:39:25.760 --> 00:39:28.110
said, 'I want to read

00:39:28.110 --> 00:39:28.120
Revelation

00:39:28.120 --> 00:39:30.230
to you,

00:39:30.240 --> 00:39:33.070
chapter

00:39:33.070 --> 00:39:33.080
8.'She

00:39:33.080 --> 00:39:35.670
said there were four angels,

00:39:35.680 --> 00:39:37.990
and

00:39:38.000 --> 00:39:40.110
seven

00:39:40.110 --> 00:39:40.120
altogether,

00:39:40.120 --> 00:39:42.670
but four first

00:39:42.680 --> 00:39:44.310
and then three

00:39:44.320 --> 00:39:46.590
for a later time.

00:39:46.600 --> 00:39:48.110
And she goes, "Do you think this is what

00:39:48.120 --> 00:39:50.790
you were seeing, honey?"I said,

00:39:50.800 --> 00:39:53.310
"I don't know, babe. All I

00:39:53.320 --> 00:39:55.150
know is I saw these angels blowing these

00:39:55.160 --> 00:39:56.910
horns and all this stuff going

00:39:56.910 --> 00:39:56.920
on."She

00:39:56.920 --> 00:39:58.390
goes, "Do you think it was the four

00:39:58.400 --> 00:40:00.190
coming out of the Euphrates River

00:40:00.190 --> 00:40:00.200
because

00:40:00.200 --> 00:40:01.950
they were

00:40:01.950 --> 00:40:01.960
water?"So,

00:40:01.960 --> 00:40:04.510
I don't know.

00:40:04.520 --> 00:40:09.270
All I know is that I am

00:40:09.280 --> 00:40:12.390
in awe.

00:40:12.400 --> 00:40:14.470
I'm in awe

00:40:14.480 --> 00:40:16.070
that God would allow me to see something

00:40:16.080 --> 00:40:18.070
like that.

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:21.750
I thought it was really cool about the

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:24.550
souls and all this stuff, but when I saw

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:26.310
all this stuff happening with the sea

00:40:26.310 --> 00:40:26.320
again—the

00:40:26.320 --> 00:40:28.390
sea—and

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:30.630
then the seas

00:40:30.640 --> 00:40:34.070
and the waves will roar.

00:40:34.080 --> 00:40:35.350
Remember that?

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:38.630
And it was above the water;

00:40:38.640 --> 00:40:41.470
it was a sound.

00:40:41.480 --> 00:40:43.990
It wasn't that they

00:40:43.990 --> 00:40:44.000
were

00:40:44.000 --> 00:40:45.750
moving;

00:40:45.760 --> 00:40:49.230
it was deafeningly loud as the angel blew

00:40:49.240 --> 00:40:54.110
his horn.

00:40:54.120 --> 00:40:56.230
It was something upon the

00:40:56.240 --> 00:41:02.550
water. It sounded like

00:41:02.560 --> 00:41:04.710
you hear a tornado

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:09.190
or a freight train.

00:41:09.200 --> 00:41:10.750
You can hear a train coming in the

00:41:10.760 --> 00:41:12.710
distance—that

00:41:12.720 --> 00:41:15.190
loud train

00:41:15.200 --> 00:41:17.190
coming,

00:41:17.200 --> 00:41:18.670
not the horn. It

00:41:18.670 --> 00:41:18.680
sounded

00:41:18.680 --> 00:41:23.350
like a loud noise,

00:41:23.360 --> 00:41:25.510
but it was deafening.

00:41:25.520 --> 00:41:27.430
It was so loud, and it was on the

00:41:27.440 --> 00:41:29.630
face of the water of the world.

00:41:29.640 --> 00:41:31.510
The seas and the waves were

00:41:31.520 --> 00:41:40.153
roaring. It was loud; it was a noise.

00:41:40.153 --> 00:41:40.163
All

00:41:40.163 --> 00:41:44.030
I

00:41:44.040 --> 00:41:48.870
know to tell you

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:53.390
is that we're running out of time.

00:41:53.400 --> 00:41:56.670
As I see these things and I see the days

00:41:56.680 --> 00:41:58.310
approach, the Lord keeps warning me

00:41:58.320 --> 00:42:00.990
to tell you over and over again: it's

00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:04.390
time for you to come to Jesus.

00:42:04.400 --> 00:42:06.110
I say it over and over again and people

00:42:06.120 --> 00:42:08.070
say, "Brandon, why do you keep doing

00:42:08.070 --> 00:42:08.080
this?"Because

00:42:08.080 --> 00:42:11.350
there's an urgency in my spirit to warn

00:42:11.360 --> 00:42:13.830
you over and over again

00:42:13.840 --> 00:42:15.710
that you're running out of time. I don't

00:42:15.720 --> 00:42:18.710
know the time frame that Jesus Christ

00:42:18.720 --> 00:42:20.230
will come. No man knows the day or the

00:42:20.240 --> 00:42:22.990
hour, but we see that the time frame is

00:42:23.000 --> 00:42:25.350
speeding up. We can see, we can feel it.

00:42:25.360 --> 00:42:30.390
There's an urgency in the air.

00:42:30.400 --> 00:42:32.790
And my question for you is: do you know

00:42:32.800 --> 00:42:36.710
him?

00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:39.110
But more importantly,

00:42:39.120 --> 00:42:41.150
does he know you?

00:42:41.160 --> 00:42:43.270
I say this over and over again because

00:42:43.280 --> 00:42:47.830
it's so important as we keep

00:42:47.840 --> 00:42:50.070
going on with this channel

00:42:50.080 --> 00:42:51.710
and the Lord keeps showing us things

00:42:51.720 --> 00:42:53.110
more and more.

00:42:53.120 --> 00:42:56.590
It shakes me, and I have such an urgency

00:42:56.600 --> 00:42:59.510
to warn the people that 2026 will be the

00:42:59.520 --> 00:43:02.590
year of 1 Corinthians

00:43:02.600 --> 00:43:10.750
5:5.

00:43:10.760 --> 00:43:13.910
And there will be so many people

00:43:13.920 --> 00:43:16.070
that have the seedtime and

00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:20.710
harvest accelerated

00:43:20.720 --> 00:43:22.430
that he doesn't want any of us to go to

00:43:22.440 --> 00:43:24.110
hell.

00:43:24.120 --> 00:43:25.870
He wants all of us to come to

00:43:25.880 --> 00:43:28.790
repentance.

00:43:28.800 --> 00:43:31.110
And it's time for the church to wake up

00:43:31.120 --> 00:43:33.230
because he said to me again,

00:43:33.240 --> 00:43:35.550
"Judgment begins in my house first.

00:43:35.560 --> 00:43:39.030
Brandon,

00:43:39.040 --> 00:43:41.350
judgment begins in my house first. It's

00:43:41.360 --> 00:43:44.310
time to come to Jesus.

00:43:44.320 --> 00:43:46.750
It's time."But he is knocking on your

00:43:46.760 --> 00:43:49.750
heart even again tonight.

00:43:49.760 --> 00:43:52.750
Do you know my friend Jesus?

00:43:52.760 --> 00:43:54.310
You may be here tonight and you say,

00:43:54.320 --> 00:43:56.310
"Brandon, I hear you and you

00:43:56.320 --> 00:43:57.750
really scared me."I'm not trying to

00:43:57.760 --> 00:44:00.030
scare you. I'm trying to prepare you.

00:44:00.040 --> 00:44:03.750
I'm trying to tell you of what's to come.

00:44:03.760 --> 00:44:05.670
And if you don't know my friend Jesus,

00:44:05.680 --> 00:44:07.630
you're in trouble.

00:44:07.640 --> 00:44:09.310
The Bible said there's no other way to

00:44:09.320 --> 00:44:12.070
the Father except through him.

00:44:12.080 --> 00:44:13.990
People said, "Brandon, I want to serve

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:16.430
Buddha and Jesus."I got the emails this

00:44:16.430 --> 00:44:16.440
way.

00:44:16.440 --> 00:44:18.910
"I want to serve Buddha and Jesus.

00:44:18.920 --> 00:44:21.710
I love Buddha and I love Jesus. Can I

00:44:21.720 --> 00:44:23.110
serve

00:44:23.120 --> 00:44:25.430
both?"And

00:44:25.440 --> 00:44:27.470
my answer to you

00:44:27.480 --> 00:44:29.910
is: no,

00:44:29.920 --> 00:44:32.349
you can't. There are no other gods

00:44:32.359 --> 00:44:33.870
before him.

00:44:33.880 --> 00:44:36.030
Even the Ten Commandments—everything that the

00:44:36.040 --> 00:44:37.990
Bible says—God is a jealous God. It's

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:41.670
all about him. You serve Jesus only.

00:44:41.680 --> 00:44:43.670
There are no other gods before him. Those

00:44:43.680 --> 00:44:45.950
are false gods. He is the one and only

00:44:45.960 --> 00:44:48.270
God. He is true God.

00:44:48.280 --> 00:44:50.390
Buddha is a false god.

00:44:50.400 --> 00:44:54.190
Muhammad is a false god.

00:44:54.200 --> 00:44:56.310
Jesus is the only way.

00:44:56.320 --> 00:44:58.950
So my answer to you is no. You cannot

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:01.710
serve Buddha and Jesus. Why would you

00:45:01.720 --> 00:45:06.470
want to? Buddha's dead. Jesus is alive.

00:45:06.480 --> 00:45:09.710
Muhammad's dead. Jesus is alive.

00:45:09.720 --> 00:45:11.790
He rose again. He died for you. He

00:45:11.800 --> 00:45:14.110
suffered greatly so that you don't have

00:45:14.120 --> 00:45:15.870
to go to hell.

00:45:15.880 --> 00:45:17.470
There's a heaven to gain and a hell to

00:45:17.480 --> 00:45:18.790
shun.

00:45:18.800 --> 00:45:22.390
You must know Jesus. It's appointed unto

00:45:22.400 --> 00:45:23.750
man once to die and after that

00:45:23.750 --> 00:45:23.760
the

00:45:23.760 --> 00:45:25.030
judgment.

00:45:25.040 --> 00:45:27.030
So my question to you tonight: do you

00:45:27.040 --> 00:45:28.230
know him?

00:45:30.480 --> 00:45:32.430
And if you don't,

00:45:35.560 --> 00:45:38.710
I want to say a simple prayer for you.

00:45:38.720 --> 00:45:40.310
It's easy.

00:45:40.320 --> 00:45:42.550
But tonight, the Lord is knocking on

00:45:42.560 --> 00:45:44.349
your heart.

00:45:44.359 --> 00:45:46.349
He's giving you an opportunity to come

00:45:46.359 --> 00:45:47.630
to him.

00:45:47.640 --> 00:45:49.950
After I tell you all that, how could you

00:45:49.960 --> 00:45:52.230
not? He loves you.

00:45:52.240 --> 00:45:54.190
He's knocking on the door of your heart.

00:45:54.200 --> 00:45:56.710
He's saying, "Will you let me in?

00:45:56.720 --> 00:45:58.310
Or will you be one of the ones that

00:45:58.320 --> 00:46:00.870
didn't open the door for

00:46:00.870 --> 00:46:00.880
him?"So,

00:46:00.880 --> 00:46:02.510
tonight, I'm going to say a simple

00:46:02.520 --> 00:46:03.750
prayer for you,

00:46:03.760 --> 00:46:07.349
but I want you to be bold about your

00:46:08.000 --> 00:46:09.230
decision.

00:46:09.240 --> 00:46:10.990
I want you to tell us in the comment

00:46:11.000 --> 00:46:12.710
section down below; tell

00:46:12.720 --> 00:46:15.349
us right now, "I want to be saved.

00:46:15.359 --> 00:46:17.310
I want Jesus to be my Lord and personal

00:46:17.320 --> 00:46:18.510
Savior.

00:46:18.520 --> 00:46:20.790
I want to sell out to him tonight.

00:46:20.800 --> 00:46:23.270
I want to turn my back on the world.

00:46:23.280 --> 00:46:26.030
I'm ready. Tonight's my

00:46:26.030 --> 00:46:26.040
night."Tonight's

00:46:26.040 --> 00:46:29.110
your night for salvation.

00:46:29.120 --> 00:46:32.710
The very shoes you put on today

00:46:32.720 --> 00:46:34.110
that you thought you were going to go home

00:46:34.110 --> 00:46:34.120
in

00:46:34.120 --> 00:46:35.510
that night, the undertaker might be

00:46:35.520 --> 00:46:37.710
taking them off that night. No one is

00:46:37.720 --> 00:46:39.510
promised tomorrow.

00:46:39.520 --> 00:46:42.670
No one is promised the next five hours from

00:46:42.680 --> 00:46:43.990
now.

00:46:44.000 --> 00:46:46.790
I'm telling you

00:46:46.800 --> 00:46:50.270
it's time to come to Jesus today. You're

00:46:50.280 --> 00:46:53.950
running out of time.

00:46:53.960 --> 00:46:56.230
So, I'm going to say a simple prayer

00:46:56.240 --> 00:46:57.830
and I want you to say it with me. Say,

00:46:57.840 --> 00:46:59.270
"Jesus,

00:46:59.280 --> 00:47:02.270
I believe you're the son of God.

00:47:02.280 --> 00:47:04.510
I believe you died for me and you rose

00:47:04.520 --> 00:47:06.950
again on the third day.

00:47:06.960 --> 00:47:09.510
Jesus, I'm a sinner

00:47:09.520 --> 00:47:11.710
and I need a savior.

00:47:11.720 --> 00:47:15.590
I want you to forgive me of my sins.

00:47:15.600 --> 00:47:18.349
Forgive me for all I've done. Forgive me

00:47:18.359 --> 00:47:20.710
for all the wrong I've done, for all the

00:47:20.720 --> 00:47:23.070
things I've done bad.

00:47:23.080 --> 00:47:26.990
Wash me. Make me clean.

00:47:27.000 --> 00:47:28.550
Jesus,

00:47:28.560 --> 00:47:31.230
from this day forward, I turn my back on

00:47:31.240 --> 00:47:32.550
the devil.

00:47:32.560 --> 00:47:35.430
I turn my back on the world. I turn my

00:47:35.440 --> 00:47:37.990
back on my sin. And from this day

00:47:38.000 --> 00:47:39.710
forward, Lord, I serve you with all my

00:47:39.720 --> 00:47:41.190
heart.

00:47:41.200 --> 00:47:43.830
I'll serve you, Father. I make you my

00:47:43.840 --> 00:47:46.270
Lord and personal Savior. From this day

00:47:46.280 --> 00:47:48.790
forward, I'm sold out

00:47:48.800 --> 00:47:50.270
to you,

00:47:50.280 --> 00:47:52.310
and I want you to be the captain of my

00:47:52.320 --> 00:47:54.430
ship.

00:47:54.440 --> 00:47:56.550
Thank you, Father.

00:47:56.560 --> 00:47:58.470
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of

00:47:58.480 --> 00:48:00.470
Life.

00:48:00.480 --> 00:48:02.150
Thank you, Lord, that you've forgiven

00:48:02.160 --> 00:48:03.630
me.

00:48:03.640 --> 00:48:05.070
Thank you, Lord, that you've given me a

00:48:05.080 --> 00:48:07.030
fresh, clean start

00:48:07.040 --> 00:48:09.830
